                '2 tablespoons Oil, 1 Onion, chopped, 4-5 garlic cloves, crushed, 2 tablespoons Grated ginger, 2 teaspoons Curry powder, 1/2 teaspoon Cumin, 1/2 teaspoon Turmeric, Salt to taste, Pepper to taste, 1 can (14oz/400g) Tomato sauce/crushed tomatoes, 3 cups (720ml) Water, 1 can (14oz/400g) Coconut milk, 1 cup (190g) Dried lentils, 1 teaspoon Garam masala (optional), 1-2 tablespoons Coriander leaves, chopped *optional',
