                'For the meat mixture: 2 tablespoons Oil, 1 pound (450g) Ground beef, 1 Onion, chopped, 1 Bell pepper, diced, 3 Garlic cloves, crushed, 1 can (400g) Crashed tomatoes, Salt to taste, Pepper to taste, 1 teaspoon Paprika, 1 teaspoon Cumin, 1 teaspoon Oregano, For serving: 12 Taco shells/Corn tortillas, Cheddar cheese, 1 Avocado, diced, 4-5 Lettuce leaves, thinly sliced, Cilantro, 1/2 Red onion, chopped',
